description:
Chatting with The Rings of Power showrunners JD Payne and Patrick McKay about Season 2, Celebrimbor, Adar, the Gandalf decision, handling criticism, and which character(s) may step up in Season 3!  And yes, I also ask what the deal was with "the kiss"...

#theringsofpower #lordoftherings #ringsofpower
title: JD Payne & Patrick McKay talk Rings of Power Season 2 and beyond...
